AB  - A set of transformations based on the Lp-norm are used to generate alternative parametric and nonparametric formulations of production frontiers. Particular attention is paid to the cases p = 1 (least absolute value estimation) and p = ∞ (Chebyshev estimation). A class of generalized transformations of inputs and outputs by using the Box-Cox transformations is also explored and illustrated.
